<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٦٨:</span> <span class="c3">{لَا تَسْمَعُ فِيهَا لَاغِيَةً}</span>: شَتْمًا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
